quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,61,"Ne olwa emikanda chibili echo chialolana, Abandu ba Musa nibaboola mbu: “Toto efwe khutililwe.”"
  26,62,"(Musa) Naboola mbu: “Shikali kario tawe. Toto Nyasaye wanje Omulesi ali halala ninasi, yetsa okhulunjisia.”"
  26,63,"Mana nikhufimbulila Musa mbu: “Khupa indabushi yiyio khu inyanza.” Mana niikabukhana, ne buli elubeka niba shinga olukulu olukhongo."
  26,64,"Mana nikhusitia hambi hao Abandu bandi abo."
  26,65,"Mana nikhuhonokosia Musa nende balia abali halala ninaye boosi."
  26,66,"Mana nikhusishilia mumatsi abandi abo."
  26,67,"Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko, halali abanji mubo shibasuubilanga tawe."
  26,68,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,69,"Ne basomele amakhuwa ka Ibrahim."
  26,70,"Olwa yaboolela papa wuwe nende Abandu bebe mbu: “Shina shiamulaamanga?”"
  26,71,"Nibaboola mbu: “Khulaamanga ebifwanani, mana khutong’e hao tsinyanga tsiosi (khubilamanga).”"
  26,72,"Naboola mbu: “Koo, bibawulilanga olwa mubilaanganga?"
  26,73,"Nohomba bibakhonyangakhwo (nimubilaama), nohomba bibawumisinjia (nimukhaya okhubilama)?""
  26,74,"Nibaboola mbu: “(Shibikholanga ako tawe) halali khwanyoola bapapa befu nibakholanga bario.”"
  26,75,"Naboola mbu: “Koo, mulolanga ebia mulaamanga ebo?"
  26,76,"Enywe nende abakofu benyu abaranjilila?"
  26,77,"Toto abo ni abasuku banje (abamulaamanga abo) halali Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,78,"Ulia owanoonga, naye niye ulunjisinjia."
  26,79,"Ne niye undisinjia khandi unywesinjia."
  26,80,"Ne nendwala, niye umboninjia."
  26,81,"Ne niye ulifwisia ne alilamusia."
  26,82,"Ne niye wesuubilanga mbu alindeshela ebionono bianje inyanga yomurungo."
  26,83,"Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, mbelesia amachesi kokhukhalaka eshina ne unde halala nende abakholi bamalayi."